{"tha-ap510:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap510:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap510:0.3":"8 Amodaphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap510:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap510:1.2":"Ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap510:1.3":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap510:1.4":"Amodamadadim phalam. ","tha-ap510:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap510:2.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap510:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap510:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap510:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap510:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap510:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap510:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap510:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap510:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap510:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap510:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap510:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap510:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma amodaphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap510:7.1":"Amodaphaliyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}